          reached:step_2
          censused,uno=6,duo=2
          see:two collections stand divided on one shared disk — each Pier holds only its own artists as whole original bytes
          reached:seal
          sealed
          reached:job_uno
          see:the pair sealed over the wire — a mutual Music grant gates the heist both ways
          see:a heist job stands pointed at the pier — its filing decisions pinned before any byte crossed
